episodes.title: I was a Jehovah's Witness. My story.
episodes.description:
Hey everyone! 
I have finally come to a place where I feel comfortable talking about my story of being a Jehovahs Witness and getting disfellowshipped.
My mom got baptized into the cult when I was 6. I got baptized when I was 16 and disfellowshipped when I was 32(I'm 39 now).
You can hear my full podcast here:
http://livehappylivehealthy.com/podcast

You can find me on Instagram 
@vevianvozmediano
